{"tid":593002,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【求屌醒】唔知點揀好","createTime":"2018-03-14T16:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T17:03:11.000Z","uid":151399,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b36060be239e4a466e5d5a7d5ba01f8f4f14ae61","tid":593002,"uid":151399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T16:17:06.000Z","msg":"我同條仔一齊咗年幾，佢係各方面都好好，但係近排發現自己好似已經唔再鍾意佢，連一齊都覺得好悶好無意思，唯一用途就係食飯或者出出入入有個人陪住。近排發現自己鍾意咗另一個出面識嘅男仔，但我地又好似無乜可能一齊，佢都唔算係自己嘅理想對象。佢就好social嘅，應該都有唔少女埋身，但係我係翻工度第一眼見到佢就已經有feel，我地好快都交換咗contact仲一路有傾，但到佢知道我有男朋友之後又冷淡咗少少，但我真係好想試下同佢一齊，雖然自己都知可能性唔高。就算一齊咗，因為係我單方面鍾意佢多啲，咁之後都未必會開心，可能好快就散。但宜家呢個真係好悶，好想試下同新嘅發展，但又唔知會有咩結果。唔知點揀，求屌醒！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99df7b78a95186be0e72e70dd3e61b18b6ee45d","tid":593002,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"你自己心入面都有答案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1e21b08c6ef265f368da430eef308b8f9566e7","tid":593002,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T16:22:30.000Z","msg":"just do it"},{"pid":"0dc3d813297fb0e8e605bc163b3c31b7c466d8b9","tid":593002,"uid":70368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T16:24:06.000Z","msg":"唔再鐘意人又唔分,拖住人咩意思<br />\n<br />\n一定要拍住拖?<br />\n無男人會死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf5e6cdedf5e132e4d6c9b10c8b182ca6077327","tid":593002,"uid":20448,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T16:38:38.000Z","msg":"三條死基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2275de6f8bc6fa0039597a6ef1eb929be6792094","tid":593002,"uid":20468,"like":0